name: Golden Time
description:
The Meeting of The Cat and The Death never felt imperfect, The perfect timing between two worlds has always been a bridge between the living and the dead.

Cat once had a really close friend. however, that friend has gone too far, Death has picked her up first. Therefore, whenever Cat get a chance to meet The Death, They always jokes around and spend some times to share one of two stories, because Cat always feel that whenever The Death is near, His friend also there to hear them.
